data.description: Energy Star ''SMART'' home on premium 1/4 acre lot with panoramic views. One owner home with engineered wood flooring, carpeted bedrooms and 10ft ceilings. Great room/Media room with in-wall AV wiring & surround sound speakers. Contemporary open floor plan. Solar with 10k Sonnen battery storage with emergency battery backup circuits. Gourmet Kitchen, Electric stove top with natural gas lines installed.. Walk In Pantry, Granite countertops with a large Island with Stainless steel appliances.  Covered back patio. Large back yard. Graded with irrigation.
